title: Re: keen babysitter music
content:
In that case, you are probably out of luck. No one's composed a MIDI version of that song yet (I don't think so. At least I didn't see any on Beyond the Pogo). And there's even less chance there's a MOD version of it.

There's some MID2MOD conversion utility I used once which worked okay for making MOD files. You could use that if you come upon a MIDI file.--------------
